name: Strawberry with Wolves #1
description:
My cat, Strawberry, adopted in spring of 2020. Any kind of meticulous work involving a number of small pieces is her area of expertise –  be it making beaded necklaces or assembling jigsaw puzzles.

I was working on this 1000 piece puzzle during the boring and mostly cold summer of 2020 while listening to YouTube lectures on psychoanalysis. Wolf Man, wolf puzzle – Strawberry is here to help.

Picture taken with FujiFilm Digital Q1, a digital camera released in 2003 with 7Mb built-in storage.

Resolution: 640x480

Summer 2020
St. Petersburg, Russia
